g.aria-label: It's impossible to tell what the speed limit is around here... if the last speed limit sign you passed was slow, then turn left and drive a block; if it was fast, veer to the right and drive two blocks. If one of the blocks now surrounding you contains an orange sign, drive another block. Repeat the following step twice: Choose a direction and drive straight, stopping immediately after passing a sign of a different color than the previous one you passed. Choose the direction such that you drive the fewest blocks doing this. If there are multiple such directions, choose the one that brings you closest to the center of the neighborhood.
